- Surprise!</i>

09:48.004 --> 09:49.916
- Happy birthday, Mom!
- Happy birthday!

09:50.006 --> 09:53.750
Oh, my God!
Miles! And Jack!

09:53.843 --> 09:57.257
What a surprise!

09:57.347 --> 10:01.182
I can't remember the last time
you brought me flowers!

10:01.267 --> 10:03.179
Happy birthday, Mom.

10:03.269 --> 10:05.135
They're from both of us.

10:05.271 --> 10:09.936
- A famous actor bringing me flowers for my birthday!
- Right? Yeah!

10:10.068 --> 10:13.652
<i>- Don't I feel special?
- And champagne!</i>

10:13.738 --> 10:16.947
- Famous actor's getting married next week, Mom.
- Oh, that's right!

10:17.033 --> 10:18.945
Isn't that nice.

10:19.035 --> 10:22.369
I hope that girl knows
how lucky she is...

10:22.455 --> 10:25.368
marrying no less
than Derek Sommersby.

10:25.458 --> 10:29.327
Gosh, that was, like, 11 years ago,
Mrs. Raymond.

10:29.462 --> 10:33.502
<i>Well, you were wonderful in that show!</i>

10:33.591 --> 10:38.837
Why that didn't make you the biggest
movie star in the world is a sin!

10:38.930 --> 10:41.388
<i>Oh, now, Miles,</i>

10:41.474 --> 10:45.514
why didn't you tell me you were coming
and bringing this handsome man?

10:45.603 --> 10:47.515
Look how
I'm dressed!

10:47.605 --> 10:50.018
I've gotta run
and put my face on.

10:50.108 --> 10:52.020
You look fabulous,
Mrs. Raymond.

10:52.110 --> 10:53.646
Oh, stop it!

10:53.736 --> 10:55.602
<i>Make yourselves comfortable.</i>

10:55.738 --> 10:58.651
<i>- You boys hungry?</i>
- Yeah, I'm hungry.

10:58.741 --> 11:01.609
<i>Along with the battle casualties...</i>

11:01.703 --> 11:03.615
Just a snack.

11:03.705 --> 11:05.617
<i>the Germans lost
almost a million men.</i>

11:05.707 --> 11:09.075
To replace them, Hitler turned
to his last resort of manpower.

11:13.965 --> 11:16.252
This is delicious, Mrs. Raymond.
Absolutely delicious.

11:16.384 --> 11:18.797
- Mmm.
- They're just leftovers.

11:18.887 --> 11:20.799
I-Is this chicken?

11:20.889 --> 11:22.801
I could have made
something fancier...

11:22.891 --> 11:25.804
if a certain someone had let me know
that a certain someone...

11:25.894 --> 11:29.854
was coming for a visit and bringing
a certain special friend.

11:29.939 --> 11:31.646
It was a surprise, Mom.

11:31.733 --> 11:34.146
And I could've already
put clean sheets...

11:34.235 --> 11:36.227
on the other bed
and the foldout.

11:36.321 --> 11:38.233
You are staying.

11:38.323 --> 11:43.193
Wendy, Ron and the twins are picking us up
at 11:30 to go to brunch at the Sheraton.

11:43.286 --> 11:45.528
They do
a magnificent job there.

11:45.622 --> 11:48.535
- You talked to Wendy?
- Just now.

11:48.625 --> 11:51.083
She's thrilled!
And the twins...

11:51.169 --> 11:53.582
<i>No, no, I bet.
I bet. Yeah.</i>

11:53.671 --> 11:57.665
Well, you know, Jack is pretty eager to,
uh, to get up to, um...

11:57.759 --> 11:59.842
<i>You know.</i>

11:59.928 --> 12:03.137
Uh, but, yeah, absolutely.
We'll see how it goes.

12:05.892 --> 12:08.100
Well, you boys
do what you want.

12:08.186 --> 12:11.896
I just thought it would be nice for us to
be together as a family on my birthday.

12:11.981 --> 12:14.268
Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.

12:15.485 --> 12:18.102
I'll be right back.

13:45.700 --> 13:48.613
And what was
that other one you did?

13:48.703 --> 13:51.116
The one where
you were the jogger.

13:51.205 --> 13:53.993
Oh, that was for, um,
Spray 'n Wash.

13:54.083 --> 13:55.995
Spray 'n Wash!
That's the one!

13:56.085 --> 14:00.170
Gosh. I remember the girl that was
in it with me. She was somethin'.

14:00.256 --> 14:03.169
<i>I just remember you jogging.</i>

14:03.259 --> 14:05.672
Whoo-hoo!

14:05.762 --> 14:08.175
<i>So, when's the wedding?</i>

14:08.264 --> 14:11.348
Next Saturday, Mom.
Remember? We told you.

14:11.434 --> 14:14.347
And Miles is my best man,
Mrs. Raymond. My main man.

14:14.437 --> 14:17.350
Miles, when are you going
to get married again?

14:19.525 --> 14:21.812
I just got divorced,
Phyllis.

14:21.903 --> 14:23.986
<i>Two years ago, buddy.</i>

14:25.073 --> 14:26.985
You should get
back together...

14:27.075 --> 14:29.317
with Victoria.

14:29.410 --> 14:32.118
She was good for you.

14:32.205 --> 14:34.993
She was good for you!

14:35.083 --> 14:37.450
And so beautiful,
and so intelligent.

14:37.543 --> 14:39.455
You knew her, right?

14:39.545 --> 14:42.379
<i>Oh, yeah. Real well.
Still do.</i>

14:43.383 --> 14:45.875
<i>I'm worried about you,
Miles.</i>

14:49.347 --> 14:51.430
Do you need some money?

14:53.726 --> 14:55.843
<i>Jack.</i>

14:57.188 --> 14:59.430
<i>Jack.</i>

14:59.524 --> 15:01.481
Jack, come on.

