helping him with his computer.

16:46.506 --> 16:51.092
Well, I say fuck therapy and...
What is that stuff you take? Xanax?

16:51.177 --> 16:53.214
And Lexapro, yes.

16:53.304 --> 16:56.672
Well, I say fuck that too.
You need to get your joint worked on, Miles.

16:56.766 --> 16:59.634
<i>Okay, Jack... Jack...</i>

16:59.727 --> 17:03.266
This week is not about me.
It is about you.

17:04.315 --> 17:07.228
I'm gonna show <i>you</i>
a good time.

17:07.318 --> 17:10.732
We're gonna drink a lot of good wine,
we're gonna play some golf,

17:10.820 --> 17:13.733
we're gonna eat some great food,
enjoy the scenery,

17:13.824 --> 17:17.192
and we're gonna send <i>you</i> off in style,
<i>mon frÃ¨re.</i>

