like,
a nutty Edam cheese.

19:19.158 --> 19:21.150
Wow.

19:21.243 --> 19:23.109
Mmm!

19:23.245 --> 19:25.111
- Strawberries. Yeah.
- Good.

19:25.247 --> 19:27.409
- Strawberries. Not the cheese.
- All right.

19:27.500 --> 19:30.413
Put your glass down.
Get some air into it.

19:30.503 --> 19:32.415
Oxygenating it
opens it up.

19:32.505 --> 19:35.122
It unlocks the aromas, the flavors.
Very important.

19:35.257 --> 19:37.624
