I am <i>not</i> drinking any fucking merlot!

39:38.459 --> 39:40.872
Okay, okay.
Relax, Miles.

39:40.962 --> 39:42.874
Jesus.
No merlot.

39:42.964 --> 39:45.126
Did you bring
your Xanax?

39:46.801 --> 39:48.713
All right.

39:48.803 --> 39:50.715
Come here.

39:50.805 --> 39:53.388
Do not drink too much.
Do you hear me?

39:53.474 --> 39:56.342
I don't want you passing out
or going to the dark side.

39:56.477 --> 39:59.311
