- Okay!

40:03.359 --> 40:06.272
Hi. Just looking
for some friends.

40:17.832 --> 40:19.744
Good evening, ladies.
How are you?

40:19.834 --> 40:21.746
- Hi, Miles.<i>
- Good. How are you?</i>

40:21.836 --> 40:25.204
Hello, Maya.

40:25.340 --> 40:28.208
- You look gorgeous. You both do.
<i>- Thank you.</i>

40:28.343 --> 40:30.960
- You're not so bad yourself.
- Thanks. Thanks.

40:31.054 --> 40:32.920
<i>So, what's good here?</i>

40:33.056 --> 40:36.265
- What is this you're drinking?
- Oh, this is the Fiddlehead sauvignon blanc.

40:36.392 --> 40:39.351
- Ah, I see. Is it good?
- Try it.

40:39.479 --> 40:42.347
- What time did you close up at Ka... Is it...
- Kalyra.

40:42.482 --> 40:46.567
- Kalyra.
- I actually got out of there pretty good, around 5:30, 6:00.

40:46.653 --> 40:49.521
<i>- Still had some stuff to do.
- Miles and I, we were...</i>

40:49.656 --> 40:52.023
- That's nice.
- It's aged 12 months in oak.

40:52.158 --> 40:54.070
- French oak.
- Sauvignon blanc?

40:54.160 --> 40:56.072
Huh. Interesting.
It's good.

40:56.162 --> 40:59.280
I know the winemaker.
She comes into the restaurant all the time.

40:59.415 --> 41:02.579
- What do you have to do to close up?
- I close up the register.

41:02.669 --> 41:06.834
Clean up, put some stuff away.
Then put the glasses out for the next day.

41:06.965 --> 41:08.957
- Right.
- Just... Small stuff.

41:09.050 --> 41:10.916
<i>Uh, hints of clove.</i>

41:11.052 --> 41:12.964
- Right?
- Yes! I know. I love that.

41:13.054 --> 41:15.296
Yeah. Mmm.

41:15.390 --> 41:17.256
Sorry. It's good.

41:17.392 --> 41:19.679
- No, no. We'll get you a glass.
- Ah! Now we're thinking.

41:19.769 --> 41:21.681
Good.
Okay.

41:21.771 --> 41:23.683
<i>Oh, that's... that...</i>

41:23.773 --> 41:26.516
Oh, he can say it,
and it's not disgusting?

41:26.609 --> 41:28.521
I didn't hear him say that.

41:28.611 --> 41:33.026
- Whenever I say something he said...
- Very good.

41:33.116 --> 41:35.529
No, actually... No. That one.
N-Not this one...

41:38.162 --> 41:40.905
<i>I'm having that too.</i>

41:41.040 --> 41:43.248
- Right?
- Oh, yes.

41:43.334 --> 41:44.950
That's what I'm saying.

41:45.044 --> 41:46.956
<i>For our soup
we ha ve corn chowder,</i>

41:47.046 --> 41:50.460
<i>and for our entrees we ha ve medallions
