41:50.550 --> 41:53.634
served with a root vegetable <i>foulon</i>
and wasabi whipped potatoes.

41:53.720 --> 41:55.586
<i>And finally...</i>

41:55.722 --> 41:58.635
<i>- I have to explain my credentials.
- Yes!</i>

41:58.725 --> 42:01.058
<i>Miles, what does this
remind you of?</i>

42:01.144 --> 42:04.057
"Red wine. Red wine."

42:04.147 --> 42:07.481
<i>He was brought up
on a lot of charges.</i>

42:09.027 --> 42:11.440
- Yeah?
- I mean, with the yellow light.

42:11.529 --> 42:13.441
Right.

42:13.531 --> 42:16.399
<i>After all, tonight we are celebrating
Miles's book deal.</i>

42:16.534 --> 42:18.446
- Published author.
- Oh! Wow!

42:18.536 --> 42:20.152
<i>Wow, Miles!</i>

42:20.246 --> 42:22.408
<i>- Ohh!
- Well, in that case...</i>

42:31.674 --> 42:35.884
And then they think you have no idea.
You have no control over it.

42:40.183 --> 42:42.095
<i>Ancient way
of treating the grape.</i>

42:42.185 --> 42:45.303
<i>Now it's a modern way
of treating the grape.</i>

42:45.396 --> 42:49.686
