a certain constant lapping.

43:05.917 --> 43:08.830
- It's not a... It's a fishing lake.
- Mm-hmm.

43:08.920 --> 43:10.832
Your lips look soft.

43:12.924 --> 43:15.837
- The whole area is...
- Oh, no. You mean, like, what it was used for?

43:15.927 --> 43:18.920
What do they call the...

43:23.559 --> 43:26.518
Malibu...
It's Malibu Canyon.

43:29.774 --> 43:32.642
I don't know what the hell
I'm trying to say.

44:05.184 --> 44:07.096
<i>Hello?</i>

44:07.186 --> 44:09.178
Victoria?

44:10.982 --> 44:12.894
Miles?

44:12.984 --> 44:16.477
Well, well, well, well, well.
Victoria. How the hell are ya?

44:17.905 --> 44:20.613
What... Uh...
What's on your mind?

44:20.700 --> 44:22.612
Oh, nothin'. I...

44:22.702 --> 44:24.910
Just heard that
you got remarried.

44:24.996 --> 44:27.204
Congratulations.
I, uh...

44:27.290 --> 44:30.203
Boy, I didn't think you had the
stomach for another go-around.

44:30.293 --> 44:32.205
Oh, Miles,
you're drunk.

44:32.295 --> 44:35.208
Oh, just a little
local pinot, you know.

44:35.298 --> 44:39.167
A little burgundy. That old CÃ´tes de Beaune.

