<i>- Where are you?</i>
- Uh, a little place in Los Olivos.

44:42.805 --> 44:45.718
New owners.
Cozy ambience, uh...

44:45.808 --> 44:49.017
Excellent food too.
You should, uh... You should try it.

44:49.103 --> 44:53.438
I thought of you at the, uh,
Hitching Post last night.

44:55.276 --> 44:57.188
Hello?

44:57.278 --> 44:59.486
- Miles, don't call me when you're drunk.
- No, it's...

44:59.572 --> 45:02.406
All right, I just...
I wanted to let you know...

45:02.491 --> 45:06.405
