51:10.526 --> 51:12.813
<i>- Ah! Well, congratulations.</i>
- Mmm.

51:12.945 --> 51:14.811
- Yeah.
- That's very good.

51:14.947 --> 51:17.234
- Well...
- That would do it. Yeah.

51:17.324 --> 51:19.236
Hmm.

51:19.326 --> 51:21.318
Mmm.

51:23.706 --> 51:25.914
Oh, wow, that's nice.
That's very good.

51:26.000 --> 51:28.913
We need to give it a minute,
