51:38.470 --> 51:40.462
Huh.

51:44.518 --> 51:46.430
Yeah. Yeah.

51:46.520 --> 51:48.933
I'd say
you're right on the money.

51:49.023 --> 51:51.390
Very good.
Nice.

51:51.525 --> 51:53.517
- Thank you.
- Mmm.

51:54.903 --> 51:57.816
Mmm!
Is that Stephanie's kid?

51:57.906 --> 51:59.772
Oh. Yeah.
That's Siena.

51:59.908 --> 52:02.742
- Oh, she's a sweetie.
<i>- Cute. Cute.</i>

52:02.828 --> 52:04.740
Where is she?

52:04.830 --> 52:06.742
<i>- She's at hergrandmother's.
- Oh.</i>

52:06.832 --> 52:09.074
<i>Steph's mom.
She spends a lot of time over there.</i>

52:09.168 --> 52:11.080
You got kids?

52:11.170 --> 52:13.036
Uh, me? No. No.

52:13.172 --> 52:16.586
No, I'd just fuck 'em up.

52:16.675 --> 52:21.261
No, that was the one unpolluted part
