52:21.347 --> 52:23.259
Yeah.
Same here.

52:23.349 --> 52:25.261
Good.

52:25.351 --> 52:27.343
Let's go in there.

52:29.229 --> 52:33.473
<i>Now, for a low, low
4.8% A.P.R. financing...</i>

52:44.703 --> 52:47.571
Looks like our friends
are really hitting it off.

52:47.706 --> 52:50.073
Yeah, I would say that.

52:50.209 --> 52:52.622
Yeah.

52:52.753 --> 52:55.666
So, what's your novel about?

52:55.756 --> 52:57.668
What's my...
Oh, brother.

52:57.758 --> 53:01.172
Well, it's, uh...
it's difficult to summarize.

53:01.261 --> 53:03.173
Um...

53:03.263 --> 53:06.176
It starts out as a kind of
first-person narrative...

53:06.266 --> 53:09.509
about a guy taking care of his father
after a stroke.

53:09.645 --> 53:12.888
- Oh.
- It's kind of based on, uh, personal experience.

53:12.981 --> 53:14.893
But only...
only loosely.

53:14.983 --> 53:16.895
What's the title?

53:16.985 --> 53:18.897
<i>The Day After Yesterday.</i>

53:18.987 --> 53:21.445
Oh.
You mean today.

53:23.450 --> 53:27.034
Um... Uh, yeah.
I mean, r-right. But it's more...

53:27.121 --> 53:30.785
So it's about, like,
death and mortality, or...

53:30.874 --> 53:33.457
Uh, yeah...

53:33.544 --> 53:35.456
Y... Not really.

53:35.546 --> 53:38.459
I, uh... It de...
It jumps around a lot.

53:38.549 --> 53:41.383
That's what it's about, in a way.
You know what I mean?

53:41.468 --> 53:44.381
You start to see everything
from the point of view of the father.

53:44.471 --> 53:47.885
And, uh, a lot of
other things happen... parallel narratives.

53:47.975 --> 53:49.887
It's kind of a mess.

53:49.977 --> 53:52.890
And then, eventually,
the whole thing sort of evolves,

53:52.980 --> 53:54.892
or devolves,

53:54.982 --> 53:57.315
into this sort of
Robbe-Grillet mystery.

53:57.401 --> 53:59.313
You know?

53:59.403 --> 54:01.395
But no real resolution.

54:01.488 --> 54:03.855
- Wow.
- It...

54:03.949 --> 54:06.942
Well, I think it's really great
you're getting it published.

54:07.035 --> 54:10.028
Really. I mean, I know
how hard it is just to write it even.

54:10.122 --> 54:12.034
Yeah.

54:12.124 --> 54:15.288
