due on Friday,

54:15.377 --> 54:18.290
and I'm freaked out about it,
just like in high school.

54:18.380 --> 54:20.463
- A paper, huh?
- Yeah.

54:20.549 --> 54:23.462
I'm going for a master's degree
in horticulture.

54:23.552 --> 54:25.885
Sorta chipping away on it.

54:26.013 --> 54:28.721
- Horticulture? Really?
- Mmm.

54:28.807 --> 54:31.845
I didn't even know
that there was a college here.

54:31.935 --> 54:35.349
Well, I commute to San Luis Obispo
twice a week.

54:35.439 --> 54:37.977
Horticulture?
Wow.

54:38.066 --> 54:41.059
So, do you want to work
in a winery or something?

54:42.154 --> 54:43.690
Maybe.

54:44.865 --> 54:46.857
Oh.

54:49.161 --> 54:51.073
Hmm.

54:51.163 --> 54:53.200
So, when can I
read your book?

